{"tid":2259732,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭月娥：12名港人是逃犯　會積極反駁外國政客指控","createTime":"2020-10-27T05:00:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T16:02:54.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"1340e428ac08ddf50db9843710b44915ab7d7bd5","tid":2259732,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:00:22.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥又回應12名港人涉嫌偷越邊境被內地扣押的事件，指他們是逃犯，強調他們在香港亦涉嫌干犯嚴重罪行，他們沒有面對獨立司法制度的審訊，而選擇潛逃，進入了內地的司法管轄區，干犯內地法律，就要面對內地的法律審訊。 <br />\n<br />\n她又指，自去年6月國際社會出現很多所謂全球運動，有人發起世界各地聲援12港人並不意外，但外國抗爭者就今次事件的演繹，並非特區政府願意見到，政府會積極反駁外國政客的指控。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2363401\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2363401&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETQKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=0b4497e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2363401</a>"},{"pid":"c7b67651f450160392698a4c93a7ce3dc0f35197","tid":2259732,"uid":11291,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:01:49.000Z","msg":"咁佳仔呢？"},{"pid":"52ad7689dc1e22f5e2e3dbb2bba698ed2c32a891","tid":2259732,"uid":96327,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:02:46.000Z","msg":"算啦 你都話唔到事"},{"pid":"60c535d5b4516962a4bcbeb60a63627eedbe9ee4","tid":2259732,"uid":12609,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:03:00.000Z","msg":"未判就做逃犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"546e655e25607dadc6201c92442793bdc76af03d","tid":2259732,"uid":286897,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:03:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d0e94fd6b081339b5c4627268210b5d3795ce59","tid":2259732,"uid":11291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:04:48.000Z","msg":"「自去年6月國際社會出現很多所謂全球運動」<br />\n<br />\n唔係因為你話搞逃犯條例邊會令到全世界人招呼你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780007feaebc9a9dfb47941492c8e3d7d4e53f1c",